Title: An alternative formulation of classical electromagnetic duality
Authors: Kang Li, Carlos M. Na\'on
Comments: 14 pages, no figures, Latex, minor corrections, references and
  acknowledgements added
Report-no: La Plata-Th 00/11
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A16 (2001) 1671-1684
\\
  By introducing a doublet of electromagnetic four dimensional vector
potentials, we set up a manifestly Lorentz covariant and SO(2) duality
invariant classical field theory of electric and magnetic charges. In our
formulation one does not need to introduce the concept of Dirac string.
